*   **$IONQ:** Dealers are heavily pinned near the $30–$32 range. A significant Call Wall at $36 acts as the primary upside barrier. The "gamma flip" at $32 is the pivot; below this, dealer hedging shifts from stabilizing (buying dips) to accelerating (selling into weakness), making the $30 Put Wall a "hard floor" that dealers will defend to avoid a cascading delta sell-off.
